description.content:
Food Delivery App -


According to "Polaris Market Research", the Global Food Service Disposable Market Size Is Expected To Reach USD 88.25 Billion By 2030, at a CAGR of 5.1% during the forecast period. As per market research, online food ordering has grown 300% faster than dine-in since 2014.


Are you looking for someone to automate your restaurant delivery or need Uber eats clone? Dont worry, You are at the correct spot! You are a part of this boom. Isnt it exciting?


Hey, This is Kunal Khurana, having more than 9+ years of hands-on experience in building food delivery app. My vast experience puts me in the right position to develop the food delivery app or food delivery website and perfect on-demand service provider apps identical to doordash , ubereats , Grubhub


What are you waiting for? We can start with a FREE CONSULTATION! **Offer Valid for TODAY ONLY!


Essential Features of Food Delivery App :


  • Profile Registration
  • Search Filters
  • On-Demand push notifications
  • Contact with delivery person/Restaurant
  • Real-time food delivery tracking
  • Simple Payment methods
  • Order history
  • In-app Messaging
  • Ratings and reviews
  • Discounts & Coupons


P.S - Always Ask Before Purchasing!
